<h1>Welcome to Finance Tracker</h1>

<p>The Finance Tracker app is a powerful and user-friendly tool designed to help users manage their stock investments and track market trends effortlessly. With features like real-time stock price updates, portfolio tracking, and a social component that allows users to follow friends and see their tracked stocks, the app provides a seamless experience for both beginner and experienced investors. Users can search for stocks, add them to their watchlist, and remove them as needed. The Finance Tracker also includes a friendship system, enabling users to connect with others, share insights, and build a community around smart investing. Whether you're monitoring your portfolio or exploring new market opportunities, this app is the perfect companion for staying on top of your finances.</p>

